Package: iotc.base.common.plots
Type: Package
Title: IOTC base functions for common data plotting and visualization
Version: 0.2.2
Author: Fabio Fiorellato <fabio.fiorellato@fao.org>
Maintainer: IOTC Secretariat <IOTC-Statistics@fao.org>
Description: Provides convenience methods to ensure standardised plots for all IOTC working party-related charts, including:
    Catch time-series as stacked bar charts
    Catch time-series as line charts, etc.
    Geospatial maps (superimposed pie charts, heatmaps etc.)
